    <stitle>10 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS FULLER RT-610 SERIES - REMOVE - CLUTCH HOUSING</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="IDcomponent" graphiccount="2">
        <title>CLUTCH HOUSING</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">For models so equipped, remove the clutch release mechanism.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the nuts from the six studs and remove the two bolts which attach the clutch housing
                to the case (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302417">Figure 17</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f1302417" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1302417" filename="../figg13/G1302417.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 17. Remove Bolts Attaching Clutch Housing to Case</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Break gasket seal and remove the clutch housing from the case (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302418">Figure 18</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f1302418" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1302418" filename="../figg13/G1302418.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 18. Remove Clutch Housing From Case</caption>
        </figure>
    </svcproc>
